You may use this software only for noncommercial purposes. A “noncommercial purpose” is one that does not involve providing goods or services for payment to others, or attempting to profit from the work of others.

### Commercial License

You may obtain a commercial license from the licensor by contacting them at the address provided at the end of this license. If you purchase a commercial license, this license does not apply.

